snippet.title: Feverdream: Rainbow Chaser (Announcement)
snippet.description:
What is this psychedelic madness? 

Take a trip into the wild world of Feverdream, a fracture in time and space, perceivable only at a level of hallucinogenic distortion. 

Play with your friends or solo against our global community of Dreamwalkers in a variety of game modes including a twist on the classic Battle Royal, the reaping and delivering of souls and a good old bounty hunt.

Will you be the first to reach the highest level of Incandescence?

Join us:  https://www.tangentuniversestudios.com/
